acceptance_criteria: "- npm run release:check passes after changelog regeneration.\\n- Clean temporary folder can install the package with pm install from the local checkout and generate a changelog.\\n- gh CLI confirms no open reported issues, no Dependabot alerts, and current Actions state.\\n- npm audit and npm outdated report no actionable findings.\\n- npm registry latest version is checked before and after publication."
