resolution: "Completed release verification for the new workflow and package state: release checks passed, dependencies and audit are clean, GitHub issue/PR/alert state was checked with gh, npm registry latest was verified, and a clean temp pm project installed the local checkout and generated a changelog."
expected_result: "Release readiness verification proves the package remains buildable, testable, auditable, installable through pm package flows, and clean against current GitHub and npm reports before publication."
actual_result: "npm run release:check passed with 18 node:test tests, npm audit --omit=dev found 0 vulnerabilities, npm outdated returned {}, gh issue list open returned [], Dependabot alerts returned [], gh secret list shows NPM_TOKEN present, npm view reports latest 2026.5.23-5 before this release, and /tmp/pm-changelog-v2026-05-23-6-local-P2eE22 generated CHANGELOG.md with the smoke item."
